beer.beer_name: Giant Naked Sky Santa Has Exploded
beer.beer_description:
If Christmas turns into an explosive familial shit show, don't give a shit, crack this open and slide into your festive mood.

This Belgian style Tripel is a celebration beer offering a mellow base of sweet malts with an addition of crushed coriander, zesty orange peel, and our secret Xmas spices. The long fermentation produces fruity esters and peppery tones for an incredible tasting experience.

Malt: Pale, Abbey, Aromatic, Triticale, Wheat, Oats

Hops: Perle, Saaz

Spice: "Juice for Good" Orange peels and our secret Xmas blend
